1
00:00:38,820 --> 00:00:40,820
=Visage and Soul=

2
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:43,040
("The Unique Her"
Trilogy on Women's Relationships)

3
00:00:44,720 --> 00:00:47,640
=Episode 19=

4
00:00:57,400 --> 00:00:58,160
Xiaoduo.

5
00:00:58,800 --> 00:00:59,600
What's wrong?

6
00:01:01,680 --> 00:01:02,480
Who did this?

7
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:04,200
It's nothing.

8
00:01:04,480 --> 00:01:06,160
I just took a fall earlier.

9
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:07,800
Don't lie to me.

10
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:09,120
This isn't the first time.

11
00:01:11,040 --> 00:01:12,400
It was Qiao Xiaomi.

12
00:01:13,880 --> 00:01:15,320
But I gave her
a hard time too.

13
00:01:16,160 --> 00:01:18,160
I slipped something extra
into her lunch today.

14
00:01:19,680 --> 00:01:22,320
She's probably gonna be stuck
on the toilet all week.

15
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:27,320
What's wrong?

16
00:01:30,600 --> 00:01:32,120
Why don't you tell your dad?

17
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:35,920
What good would that do?

18
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:38,480
We're adults now.

19
00:01:38,480 --> 00:01:40,200
We handle our own problems.

20
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:47,720
Xiaoduo.

21
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:49,920
One day, I'll take you away from here.

22
00:01:54,240 --> 00:01:55,520
Are you

23
00:01:56,360 --> 00:01:57,800
confessing to me?

24
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:00,840
I'll take good care of you.

25
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:04,240
Don't make promises you can't keep.

26
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:06,120
Life is long.

27
00:02:06,600 --> 00:02:08,640
Who knows who'll be taking care
of who later on?

28
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:12,480
So...

29
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:14,760
So does that mean yes?

30
00:02:17,640 --> 00:02:18,480
You tell me.

31
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:47,440
Xiaomi!

32
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:48,920
Calm down.

33
00:02:48,920 --> 00:02:49,760
Xiaomi!

34
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:56,840
Don't be scared.

35
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:58,600
Take my hand.

36
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:00,880
I'll take you somewhere safe.

37
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,000
Ye Xiaoduo.

38
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:07,000
I'm sorry.

39
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:11,800
I'm sorry.

40
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:16,120
Why are you apologizing to yourself?

41
00:03:17,440 --> 00:03:18,280
I'm sorry.

42
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,160
I'm sorry.

43
00:03:20,160 --> 00:03:21,480
Shut up!

44
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,040
Just like you asked,

45
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:49,040
I've brought them all here.

46
00:03:49,040 --> 00:03:51,320
Ask whatever you want
and get it over with.

47
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:54,360
I asked you all here today

48
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:57,040
because I want to know
what happened back then.

49
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,560
I know

50
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:00,680
I was selfish

51
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:02,000
and hurt a lot of people.

52
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:03,960
But I still want to know

53
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,680
what exactly I did back then,

54
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:06,640
and...

55
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:10,280
how I hurt Ye Xiaoduo.

56
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:16,160
She's already gone.

57
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:17,520
And back then,

58
00:04:17,520 --> 00:04:18,640
all of us got punished

59
00:04:18,640 --> 00:04:20,360
for bullying a classmate.

60
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:22,320
We paid the price we deserved.

61
00:04:22,880 --> 00:04:25,200
Can't we just leave the past
in the past?

62
00:04:27,280 --> 00:04:28,440
I want to know.

63
00:04:28,960 --> 00:04:29,720
Thank you, all of you.

64
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:32,720
Do you really want to know?

65
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:41,120
Yes.

66
00:04:42,080 --> 00:04:43,760
I pushed her and insulted her.

67
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,280
But do you think I wanted to?

68
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:48,120
Back then, you were way above us.

69
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,520
The Qiao family's precious daughter.

70
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:51,120
How could we dare go against you?

71
00:04:51,760 --> 00:04:52,800
If we didn't do what you wanted,

72
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:54,760
we would've ended up
just like Ye Xiaoduo.

73
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:56,120
Qiao Xiaomi,

74
00:04:56,840 --> 00:04:58,440
how could you forget all that?

75
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:08,840
Hey!

76
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:09,880
Move!

77
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:14,360
Every time I see you now,

78
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:15,840
I think about
how badly we treated

79
00:05:15,840 --> 00:05:17,680
Ye Xiaoduo back then.

80
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:23,080
So everything that's happened
to you today

81
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:24,960
is your punishment.

82
00:05:30,760 --> 00:05:31,480
Is...

83
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:34,920
is everything you're saying true?

84
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:37,240
One time, I didn't do what you wanted.

85
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:38,520
I refused to skip class with you.

86
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:40,280
Then your brother got some thugs

87
00:05:40,280 --> 00:05:41,760
to corner me in an alley.

88
00:05:41,760 --> 00:05:43,480
I was so scared I almost cried.

89
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:44,680
Hey, little girl.

90
00:05:45,280 --> 00:05:47,520
You went out
without any cash on you?

91
00:05:47,520 --> 00:05:48,400
Where's the money?

92
00:05:48,400 --> 00:05:49,240
Cat got your tongue?

93
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:50,280
Mr. Chen!

94
00:05:50,280 --> 00:05:51,360
Those thugs are over here!

95
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:52,000
Come quick!

96
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:52,400
Run!

97
00:05:59,200 --> 00:06:00,200
Ye Xiaoduo.

98
00:06:03,320 --> 00:06:04,880
I used to bully you.

99
00:06:04,880 --> 00:06:06,560
Why did you save me?

100
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:19,160
I know you were forced into it too.

101
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:21,000
Don't do that again.

102
00:06:22,440 --> 00:06:24,880
That's when Ye Xiaoduo saved me.

103
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,360
That's why I said

104
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:31,000
you're not even worthy
to carry her shoes.

105
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:33,040
One time, I had a fever

106
00:06:33,320 --> 00:06:34,600
and couldn't help you
copy your homework.

107
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:36,920
You threw my backpack
into the lotus pond.

108
00:06:37,320 --> 00:06:39,360
When I got home,
my dad beat me for it.

109
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:43,360
Then why didn't you fight back?

110
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:44,720
Would it have made any difference?

111
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:46,000
Your dad was rich.

112
00:06:46,400 --> 00:06:48,120
Your brother was a notorious thug.

113
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:49,320
You were pretty,

114
00:06:49,320 --> 00:06:50,280
and an excellent student.

115
00:06:50,640 --> 00:06:52,480
Half the boys in school liked you.

116
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:54,280
All you had to do was lift a finger,

117
00:06:54,280 --> 00:06:55,600
and they'd do whatever you wanted.

118
00:06:56,280 --> 00:06:57,920
We never stood a chance against you.

119
00:06:58,520 --> 00:06:59,360
That's why,

120
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:01,920
when we heard Ye Xiaoduo
had taken your boyfriend,

121
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:03,200
none of us were surprised.

122
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,200
That was probably

123
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:05,800
the strongest way
she could fight back against you.

124
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:09,720
We all did things that hurt her.

125
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:11,440
If we ever got the chance,

126
00:07:11,440 --> 00:07:13,320
we really should tell her we're sorry.

127
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,400
Especially you,

128
00:07:14,400 --> 00:07:15,360
Qiao Xiaomi.

129
00:07:45,160 --> 00:07:46,000
I'm sorry.

130
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:46,880
I'm late.

131
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:49,400
I'm Qin Yu.

132
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:51,240
I've come back to marry you.

133
00:07:52,280 --> 00:07:53,360
For three years,

134
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:55,080
I've missed you every single day.

135
00:07:56,080 --> 00:07:57,040
Was the old me

136
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:59,040
really that awful?

137
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:01,200
You are the kindest,

138
00:08:01,520 --> 00:08:02,400
sweetest girl

139
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:03,840
I've ever met in this world.

140
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:06,240
Whether in the past or now.

141
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:08,600
I know what you're afraid of.

142
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:11,720
But I'm here now.

143
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,080
From this day forward,

144
00:08:14,840 --> 00:08:16,280
you don't have
to be afraid of anything.

145
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:18,440
I'm sorry.

146
00:08:19,320 --> 00:08:20,400
I forgive you.

147
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:21,400
I swear,

148
00:08:21,640 --> 00:08:23,760
from beginning to end,
you were the only girl I ever loved.

149
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:24,560
Even after we broke up,

150
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:25,520
I never got involved with anyone else.

151
00:08:25,520 --> 00:08:26,200
Alright.

152
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:28,160
Back then, you were way above us.

153
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:29,400
The Qiao family's precious daughter.

154
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,720
If we didn't do what you wanted,

155
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:32,680
we would've ended up
just like Ye Xiaoduo.

156
00:08:33,520 --> 00:08:34,560
Your dad was rich.

157
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:36,760
Your brother was a notorious thug.

158
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:38,880
We never stood a chance against you.

159
00:08:39,920 --> 00:08:40,680
Qiao Xiaomi,

160
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:42,720
how could you forget all that?

161
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:45,760
When we heard Ye Xiaoduo
had taken your boyfriend,

162
00:08:45,760 --> 00:08:47,080
none of us were surprised.

163
00:08:47,520 --> 00:08:48,120
That was probably

164
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:49,720
the strongest way
she could fight back against you.

165
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:22,960
Qin Yu!

166
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,680
Qin Yu, save me!

167
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:26,600
Qin Yu!

168
00:09:31,560 --> 00:09:32,360
Xiaomi!

169
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:32,760
What...

170
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:33,760
What's wrong?

171
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:36,920
Who am I?

172
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:40,120
Where is this?

173
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:41,680
It's okay. Don't be scared.
I'll get you out of here.

174
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:44,320
Who am I?

175
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,560
Tell me!

176
00:09:53,400 --> 00:09:54,800
You're Qiao Xiaomi.

177
00:09:58,320 --> 00:10:00,160
Who am I really?

178
00:10:00,640 --> 00:10:01,400
Xiaoduo!

179
00:10:28,280 --> 00:10:29,320
Did I...

180
00:10:30,920 --> 00:10:32,840
see something I shouldn't have seen

181
00:10:35,160 --> 00:10:36,920
and hear something
I shouldn't have heard?

182
00:10:55,840 --> 00:10:56,760
Was she

183
00:10:58,760 --> 00:11:00,640
even prettier in person
than in the painting?

184
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:06,280
When she died, were you heartbroken?

185
00:11:13,400 --> 00:11:15,240
She was the one you called

186
00:11:17,040 --> 00:11:18,120
the kindest,

187
00:11:20,560 --> 00:11:22,240
sweetest girl.

188
00:11:25,280 --> 00:11:26,120
Wasn't she?

189
00:11:58,406 --> 00:12:00,476
♪We say good morning, we say good night♪

190
00:12:00,476 --> 00:12:03,896
♪We say we miss each other,
but never speak of the hurt♪

191
00:12:05,496 --> 00:12:07,386
♪The sweeter it is, the luckier we seem♪

192
00:12:07,386 --> 00:12:11,376
♪Yet the more romantic,
the rougher the road♪

193
00:12:12,616 --> 00:12:14,476
♪Let me go, set me free♪

194
00:12:14,476 --> 00:12:18,516
♪Let me drown in reckless silence♪

195
00:12:19,056 --> 00:12:24,466
♪We were perfect for each other,
yet you never admitted it♪

196
00:12:25,816 --> 00:12:27,956
♪The freedom you gave me♪

197
00:12:27,956 --> 00:12:31,596
♪Became the heaviest chain I bear♪

198
00:12:32,856 --> 00:12:35,126
♪Love can barely move forward♪

199
00:12:35,126 --> 00:12:38,906
♪Yet the words still linger unspoken♪

200
00:12:40,006 --> 00:12:42,246
♪The closeness I long for♪

201
00:12:42,246 --> 00:12:46,636
♪There's no need for you
to keep avoiding it♪

202
00:12:47,046 --> 00:12:48,866
♪I don't want to break free♪

203
00:12:48,866 --> 00:12:54,236
♪Take back the chains
disguised as freedom♪
